overview: Owners Kara (Dee Williams) and Evan (Ryan McLane) take a wild "ride" in the saddle barn before leaving Juliette (Whitney Wright) in charge of their vacation ranch for the weekend. Being the perfect hostess, Juliette goes out of her way to make sure all the guests have the time of their lives. When Tanya (Ryan Keely) and Bryan (Codey Steele) arrive for a badly-needed mini vacation, Juliette shows them just how accommodating she can be... joining them for an unforgettable threesome.
title: Double Booked 2: Ranch Vacation
